nmental removal rather than the capture operation that the proposition explicitly excludes. Given the specificity of the edge case language and the consistent characterization of this as a capture/extraction operation throughout the official sources, I cannot find that the plaintiff has met their burden.\n\nI will vote that the proposition has **not been demonstrated**."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019f165a539c0a8383aa27cc314cbc6d","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_sub"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_sub","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782786426094,"responseId":"gen-1782786426-Ba7awF7fkyZaTYdEbvdF"}}
